name: INAUGURAL FLIGHT | VivaAerobús A320-232 [XA-VAE] Landing at Calgary Airport
description:
Always nice to see a new airline here! Here we have the first flight of the season from VivaAerobús, a Mexican low-cost carrier operating the first charter this winter for Sunwing Vacations from San Jose del Cabo (SJD). The flight operates once a week, on Saturdays, until when, I'm not sure. VivaAerobús does have a few A320neos in their fleet; hopefully one of those makes an appearance! Enjoy my first catch of this airline, as well as its first ever visit to YYC Calgary International Airport, with ATC!

Thanks for watching!
